<og:title>New Device Heals Wounds, Replaces Stitches, Staples - Geek.com</og:title>
<og:description>You ever watch old science fiction movies and shows and marvel at how they handle medical things? Quick zap and boom! Your injury is all healed up. Well, unfortunately, we don’t live in …</og:description>
<og:url>https://www.geek.com/science/new-device-heals-wounds-replaces-stitches-staples-1722379/</og:url>
