&lt;article readability=&quot;48.079306071871&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Do you have a game you’re dying to make? Ready to jump in with both feet, and make a game for smartphones, tablets, and PCs? For a limited time, you can snag the AppGameKit game engine, numerous add-ons, and a tutorial for a great price on StackSocial.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
