&lt;p&gt;Normally, you’d have to pay $174.96 for the engine, VR add-on, royalty-free sound library, and guide, but StackSocial has a massive $144.97 discount available for the next few days. And since it’s covered by StackSocial’s own 15-Day satisfaction guarantee, you can return it for store credit if it doesn’t work out for you.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;#13;
