<og:description>Star Wars: The Last Jedi isn’t out yet, but Rian Johnson already has his next project lined up. From the looks of things the director is going to stick around the Star Wars universe …</og:description>
<og:url>https://www.geek.com/movies/rian-johnson-will-create-a-new-star-wars-trilogy-new-tv-series-also-coming-1722263/</og:url>
