<og:title>Yes, You Too Can Learn Kanji With This Candy Poo Inside of You - Geek.com</og:title>
<og:description>Have you ever learned anything from a pile of poop? You just might, if you’re working with Professor Poop, a cartoonish piece of poo that Japanese learners are bonkers for. Back in the …</og:description>
<og:url>https://www.geek.com/culture/yes-you-too-can-learn-kanji-with-this-candy-poo-inside-of-you-1722127/</og:url>
